{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8108","title":"NG8108: ngSkipHydration should be a static attribute\n\nngSkipHydration 應該是靜態屬性","contents":"<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8108.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8108-ngskiphydration-should-be-a-static-attributengskiphydration-應該是靜態屬性\">NG8108: ngSkipHydration should be a static attribute\n\nngSkipHydration 應該是靜態屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8108#ng8108-ngskiphydration-should-be-a-static-attributengskiphydration-應該是靜態屬性\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"說明\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8108#說明\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8108#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\"><code>ngSkipHydration</code> 是一個特殊的屬性，它告訴 Angular 不要讓某些特定元件參與水合。此診斷可確保靜態設定此屬性 <code>ngSkipHydration</code> 並將值設定為 <code>\"true\"</code> 或空值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The <code>ngSkipHydration</code> is a special attribute that indicates to Angular that a particular component should be\nopted-out of hydration. This diagnostic ensures that this attribute <code>ngSkipHydration</code> is set statically and the\nvalue is either set to <code>\"true\"</code> or an empty value.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-should-i-do-instead\" translation-result=\"on\">我該怎麼辦？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8108#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What should I do instead?<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8108#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 <code>ngSkipHydration</code> 時，請確保將其設定為靜態屬性（即不要使用 Angular 範本繫結語法）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When using the <code>ngSkipHydration</code>, ensure that it's set as a static attribute (i.e. you do not use the Angular template binding syntax).</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"html\" language=\"html\">\n&lt;my-cmp ngSkipHydration /&gt;\n&lt;!-- or --&gt;\n&lt;my-cmp ngSkipHydration=\"true\" /&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有關更多資訊，請參閱<a href=\"extended-diagnostics#configuration\">擴充診斷配置</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">See <a href=\"extended-diagnostics#configuration\">extended diagnostic configuration</a> for more info.</p>\n\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics#configuration\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8108#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8108#ng8108-ngskiphydration-should-be-a-static-attributengskiphydration-應該是靜態屬性\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8108#what-should-i-do-instead\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8108#我該怎麼辦\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8108#說明\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8108.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}